## Practice Task 1: Gold/Silver/Bronze Segmentation

```python
from pyspark.sql import SparkSession
from pyspark.sql.functions import when, col

spark = SparkSession.builder.appName("Bucketing Segmentation").getOrCreate()

data = [
    (1, "Rahul", 12000),
    (2, "Sneha", 8000),
    (3, "Arjun", 3000),
    (4, "Priya", 15000),
    (5, "Kiran", 5000)
]

columns = ["customer_id", "customer_name", "total_spend"]

df = spark.createDataFrame(data, columns)

df = df.withColumn(
    "segment",
    when(col("total_spend") > 10000, "Gold")
    .when((col("total_spend") >= 5000) & (col("total_spend") <= 10000), "Silver")
    .otherwise("Bronze")
)

df.show()
```

