## Practice Task 3: Quantile-Based Segmentation

```python
quantiles = df.approxQuantile("total_spend", [0.33, 0.66], 0)

q1 = quantiles[0]
q2 = quantiles[1]

df_quantile = df.withColumn(
    "quantile_segment",
    when(col("total_spend") <= q1, "Low")
    .when((col("total_spend") > q1) & (col("total_spend") <= q2), "Medium")
    .otherwise("High")
)

df_quantile.show()
```

