## Practice Task 4: Compare Different Methods

Fixed threshold segmentation uses predefined business rules. For example, spending above 10,000 is Gold.

Quantile-based segmentation depends on the data distribution. It divides customers into groups based on their relative position in the dataset.

Bucketizer is more suitable for machine learning pipelines because it converts values into numerical bucket indexes.

